import Fermat.Irregular.CircularUnits

/-!
# The circular-unit matrix at exponent 67

The uploaded `32 × 32` residue-symbol matrix is certified by an explicit
inverse over `ZMod 67`.  Matrix multiplication is substantially smaller than
expanding the determinant.  As in the exponent-37 development, this proves
the abstract lattice-index consequence once the entries are realized by
actual residue-symbol homomorphisms; it does not silently assume the missing
Sinnott--Kummer index formula.
-/

